    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the \"sustainable practices\" part but for a small shop it's not just a little investment, it's literally their whole margin. are there any specifics on how the compliance costs compare to the actual environmental benefits? like is there any data on whether these rules actually do much vs just being a huge drain on local business?",
